| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3316 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ad06178e-a72e-51f5-95d8-9fbf5ff67e65"
